CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of woman in African dress, and seven men, including Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence, standing in Office of the Mayor, City County Building
